queryItem.name: Month_desc
queryItem.expression: Case ([Import layer].[DateDim].[Month] ) When (1) Then ('January') When (2) Then ('Febuary') When (3) Then ('March') When (4) Then ('April') When (5) Then ('May') When (6) Then ('June') When (7) Then ('July') When (8) Then ('August') When (9) Then ('September') When (10) Then ('October') When (11) Then ('November') Else ('December') End

queryItem.name: Quarter_desc
queryItem.expression: If([Import layer].[DateDim].[Quarter] =1 ) Then ('Quarter-1') Else If([Import layer].[DateDim].[Quarter] =2) Then ('Quarter-2') Else If([Import layer].[DateDim].[Quarter] =3) Then ('Quarter-3') Else ('Quarter-4')

filter.name: Current Quarter
filter.expression: ([Import layer].[Emp_By_Month].[Year] = extract(year,current_date)) and ([Import layer].[Emp_By_Month].[Quarter] = (If(Cast(extract(month,current_date), integer)>=1 and Cast(extract(month,current_date), integer)<=3) Then(1) Else If(Cast(extract(month,current_date), integer)>=4 and Cast(extract(month,current_date), integer)<=6) Then(2) Else If(Cast(extract(month,current_date), integer)>=7 and Cast(extract(month,current_date), integer)<=9) Then(3) Else If(Cast(extract(month,current_date), integer)>=10 and Cast(extract(month,current_date), integer)<=12) Then(4) Else (null)))
